{
  "texts": [
    "To select the most relevant note chunks for our information extraction task, we perform cosine similarity to measure the alignment of each note chunk against the target entity's definition embedding.",
    "We retrieved the top-k (where k = 3, 5, 10) note chunks based on cosine similarity scores.",
    "For notes with fewer than k chunks, we retrieved all chunks.",
    "The retrieved chunks were passed to an LLM for the information extraction task.",
    "For notes with multiple chunks, we aggregated the LLM labels from these chunks to generate a final label for the note."
  ]
}